    "intro": "Interpretation asks what the text means — moving from observation (what does it say?) to discerning the author's intent in his original context. The movements below trace the psalm's argument from the opening petition through the bold confident close. Where the Hebrew shapes the shade of an English word, a brief note follows the interpretation as supplement.",
